  m_Name: L1009_ErrorOnDamage
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  exerciseNumber: 09
  exerciseName: ErrorOnDamage
  exerciseTitle: Error on Damage
  videoWalkthroughUrl: https://unitycodemonkey.teachable.com/courses/problem-solving/lectures/63458638
  exerciseText: Throwing error when taking damage
  hintText: Follow the Error to locate the problem, then think about how Events work.
  solutionText: 'Events need to be checked for null before invoking. If there is
    no listener then the event is set to null.

    So either manually compare it
    with null or use the Null Conditional Operator

    OnHealthAmountChanged?.Invoke(this,
    EventArgs.Empty);'
